      "More than 90% of installed US payment terminals supported contactless by the end of 2025.",
      "Visa reported 200% year-over-year growth in Tap to Phone adoption worldwide, turning ordinary smartphones into payment terminals.",
      "Nearly 85% of European retail transactions are now contactless; Australia leads with 94% tap-and-go usage.",
