    "contentMarkdown": "Buy-now-pay-later has consolidated around a handful of major players, and Klarna and Afterpay remain the two most recognizable brands for merchants choosing between global reach and category-specific strength.\n\n## Scale and reach\n\n**Klarna** reports 118 million active consumers worldwide, 966,000 merchants, and $127.9 billion in GMV for FY2025, with 55 million+ monthly active app users processing 3.4 million transactions per day. **Afterpay** reports 24 million+ active customers and 348,000+ global merchants, with $8.24 billion in Q3 2024 gross payments volume, up 23% year over year.\n\n## Market share by region\n\nIn the **US**, the two are close: Afterpay holds about **21.9%** of BNPL market share versus Klarna's **26.2%**. In **Oceania**, Afterpay is dominant with roughly **65.78%** share — reflecting its Australian roots (as Afterpay/Clearpay) versus Klarna's European base.\n\n## Product philosophy\n\nAfterpay deliberately keeps its product simple: four equal installments, always interest-free for the consumer, on a biweekly cadence, with no longer-term financing add-ons. Klarna offers broader product breadth — including longer installment plans and financing beyond the classic \"pay in 4\" — which gives it an edge in higher-ticket and European commerce.\n\n## Fees and merchant economics\n\nBoth platforms charge merchants in a similar **4-6% per-transaction range** depending on volume tier and product, and both apply a **$15 chargeback fee**.\n\n## Which one wins for which use case\n\nMerchants prioritizing simplicity, fashion/apparel/beauty categories, or an Australia/New Zealand customer base tend to see stronger performance with Afterpay. Merchants wanting broader geographic coverage, higher-ticket financing options, and deeper European penetration typically lean toward Klarna. Many large retailers now offer both to maximize checkout conversion across customer preferences.\n\n## Sources\n\n[PrimeWay FCU: Klarna vs Afterpay vs Affirm 2026](https://www.primewayfcu.com/blog/buy-now-pay-later-comparison), [Primer: Klarna vs Afterpay for Merchants](https://primer.io/blog/klarna-vs-afterpay-for-merchants), [Contra Collective: Klarna vs Afterpay BNPL 2026](https://contracollective.com/blog/klarna-vs-afterpay-bnpl-ecommerce-merchants-2026)."
